sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as llama-stack-k8s-operator<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(in-process)
    participant LlamaServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant ODHConfig as odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap
    participant UserCM as User ConfigMaps<br/>(caBundle, userConfig)
    participant IngressCtrl as Ingress Controller<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over Admin, LlamaServer: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (controller-runtime)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Get LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)

    Operator->>Operator: Check feature flags<br/>(llama-stack-operator-config)

    opt CA Bundle Aggregation (Flow 3)
        Operator->>UserCM: DirectGet user caBundle ConfigMap<br/>Kubernetes API / TLS 1.2+
        UserCM-->>Operator: CA certificates (PEM)
        Operator->>ODHConfig: DirectGet odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>Kubernetes API / TLS 1.2+
        ODHConfig-->>Operator: ODH trusted CA certs (PEM)
        Operator->>Operator: Validate X.509 certs<br/>(max 10MB, max 1000 certs)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update {instance}-ca-bundle ConfigMap
    end

    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests from base YAML
    Kustomize->>Kustomize: Apply plugins:<br/>NamePrefix → Namespace →<br/>FieldMutator → NetworkPolicy
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered Kubernetes resources

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Deployment (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Service (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply ServiceAccount (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply PVC (create only)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply NetworkPolicy (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply PDB (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply HPA (SSA)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply RoleBinding (SSA)

    opt exposeRoute=true
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Ingress (SSA)
    end

    Note over Operator, LlamaServer: Status Probing

    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP (plaintext)
    LlamaServer-->>Operator: Version info

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>(health, providers, version)

    Note over Client, LlamaServer: Flow 2: External Client Access (exposeRoute=true)

    Client->>IngressCtrl: HTTP request<br/>80/TCP
    IngressCtrl->>LlamaServer: Forward to {instance}-service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    LlamaServer-->>IngressCtrl: Response
    IngressCtrl-->>Client: HTTP response
